            The
estate tax is progressive --that is, the tax rate is higher on larger
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">estates</ENAMEX>. The first <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$600,000</NUMEX> is exempt. A <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">couple</ENAMEX> can, therefore, pass on <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$1.2</NUMEX>
