<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">opponents</ENAMEX> of the estate tax include <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">farmers</ENAMEX> . Family <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">farmers</ENAMEX> often
